snippet.title: The Quell Logic Collection - Trailer
snippet.description:
One of the world's most tranquil gaming experiences finally arrives on PC.

Over 4 million gamers have already embraced the mobile charms of this perfectly balanced break from relentless high octane titles. Now, The Quell Logic Collection offers hundreds of serenely polished puzzles that will transport PC players to a new level of calm.

Available now on Green Man Gaming - http://www.greenmangaming.com/s/gb/en/pc/games/puzzle/quell-logic-collection/

Also available on Steam and Humble Store.

Developed by Fallen Tree Games - http://www.fallentreegames.com/
Published by Green Man Loaded - http://www.greenmanloaded.com/
